    <strong>ðŸ’¡ Tip:</strong> The <a href="<%= my_wakatime_setup_path %>">setup page</a> does everything for you. No hard stuff to figure out!
  </p>


  <h3>ðŸ”Œ What Code Editors Work</h3>
